    "To exemplify how SpatialData can be used to transfer spatial annotations between datasets, we considered the masks from Visium capture locations and aggregated cell-type information from the overlapping Xenium cells to estimate cell-type fractions at each location.",
    "For comparison we also considered a deconvolution-based analysis of Visium counts (using cell2location 20) with the same scRNA-seq-derived cell types 19 as reference.",
